Package: pantomath
Version: 1.4.1
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: python3, python3-venv
Maintainer: Pantomath Project <noreply@example.com>
Description: Threat Intelligence RSS Feed Dashboard
 Pantomath aggregates threat intel RSS/Atom feeds into a live-updating
 local web dashboard. Add and remove feed sources from the UI; new
 items push to the dashboard in real time over WebSocket. Ships with
 zero pre-loaded sources — you choose everything it watches.
